728670f-a.folder: Center Street & St. Patricks Place, Staten Island, NY
728670f-a.original_title: Richmond: Center Street - St. Patricks Place
728670f-a.text:
256 Center Street, at the S.E. corner of St. Patricks Place, showing St. Patricks Academy. In 1874 this was the D. H. Cortelyou house. The view is eastward
along denter Street.
June 13, 1927
P. L. Sperr
(2)
Another view of St. Patricks Academy, and St. Patricks Roman Catholic Church on St. Patricks Place.
May 5, 1930
P. L. Sperr
(3)
The same as View B, at a later date.
May 6, 1936
P. L. Sperr

728676f-a.original_title: Richmond: Center Street - St. Patricks Place
728676f-a.text:
Center Street, east from St. Patricks Place (Richmond). In the center, on the right, is the Hkltmnn Bakery at No. 240.
